casebody.data:
Kruse Cash Register Co., Appellant, v. Byrne, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

June 29, 1892.) Appeal from fourth district court. Action by the Kruse Cash Register Company against Peter J. Byrne.

Argued before Bischoff and Giegerich, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, costs to appellant to abide the event.
